<p>
He was an associate editor of VLDB Journal,
Springer's Distributed and Parallel Databases and,
IEEE Transactions on Knowledge and Data Engineering,
Editor-in-Chief of IEEE Transactions on Knowledge and Data
Engineering (TKDE), 2009-2012,
founding co-Editor-in-Chief of 
<a href=https://www.journals.elsevier.com/big-data-research/editorial-board>
Elsevier Journal of Big Data Research</a>, 2013-2015.
associate editor of IEEE Transactions on Cloud Computing (TCC)
and the founding Editor-in-Chief of 
