<p>
He had served as a co-chair of the
<a href=http://www.sigmod.org/awards/dissertation.html>
ACM SIGMOD Jim Gray Best Thesis Award </a> committee, 2008-2011,
a trustee of VLDB endowment, 2006-2017, as its secretary, 2010-2013,
