ComfortDelgro</a> and
<a href= 
https://www.vicom.com.sg/About/Board-Of-Directors>
VICOM</a>.
He served as a
member of <a href=http://biz.zjol.com.cn/zjjjbd/cjxw/201709/t20170927_5227084.shtml>
